title: (PSX-PSP) Warcraft II: The Dark Saga converted properly (Kingdom
description:
WARCRAFT II - THE DARK SAGA:

Blizzard quickly became one of the most famous software developers ever after releasing War Craft II on the PC. Now, the adventure comes home with WAR CRAFT II: The Dark Saga, for the PlayStation. The game is a real-time strategy that takes the genre to new heights by introducing new concepts that help to make the game easy to learn, yet difficult to master. The story is about a group of orcs and humans who are battling for control of the world. Each mission brings one side one step closer to complete victory, and the game lets players choose who they wish to take sides with. The PSX version even features some enhancements over its computer counterpart, making the gameplay more fluid while lessening any frustration over completing tasks that take too much time. WAR CRAFT II: The Dark Saga contains an involving story, along with some of the most addictive play for a strategy game.


Tested and working properly on CFW 5.00 m33-4 combined with the 500 popsloader pack on 3.72 POPS.....KloWn
